#/
#/ Give waybar some time to start so systray is
#/ available when auostarting apps


# Workspaces

## Background

### Cloud-Services
exec sh -c "sleep 2" && exec pcloud
exec sh -c "sleep 2" && megasync
exec sh -c "sleep 2" && dropbox start

